thumb.title: 【歌ってみた】独りんぼエンヴィー【寺月哲夫】
thumb.description: Hi, it's Tetsuo Teratsuki. Nice to meet you.This is my first cover song in public. Finally I posted the first cover myself.I still practicing the breathing control. I planned to start with Vocaloid songs, but it's easier for me to sing in English.This song is darker for me, but little closer for my genre theme. I hope you enjoy this. That's the legend.Original MV: https://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm19466301Vocal/mix/encode by Tetsuo Teratsuki (寺月哲夫)My followed work: https://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm45039581
